---

<Section color="orange">
    <h1 class="mobile">Ben<br />Holmes</h1>
    <ul role="list">
        <li><a href="https://github.com/bholmesdev">Web dev</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://wtw.dev">Whiteboardist</a></li>
        <li><a href="#speaker">Speaker</a></li>
